{"tid":2319600,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方就9月一宗油塘海岸對開浮屍案 呼籲市民提供資料","createTime":"2020-12-10T08:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T05:22:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e2adfba1d5097e48dc944f57a0845b007a497efb","tid":2319600,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲市民就9月23日觀塘區一宗屍體發現案提供資料。<br />\n  <br />\n警方在當日上午約8時半接報，一名女子在油塘海岸對開海面漂浮，女子被救起後，現場證實死亡。<br />\n  <br />\n警方相信死者是一名年約20至40歲女子，身高約1.6至1.7米，中等身材，短黑髮，身上有3個紋身，分別位於右肩、腹部和右大腿。被發現時身穿藍白色格仔長背心，黑色長袖外套，黑色長褲，白色平底鞋及有一個深啡色手袋，身上沒有身份證明文件。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲認識死者或有案件資料提供的人士，與警方聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564614-20201210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564614-20201210.htm&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=3f132d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564614-20201210.htm&h=779bc9ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564614-20201210.htm</a>"},{"pid":"84f1ec5920f042c1e4cb415102ebd9b7c5f386f4","tid":2319600,"uid":191926,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"提供資料=知道太多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0538330e1ebc387a133799969e51bed301444062","tid":2319600,"uid":196329,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd2fe627529ef91b51f5a27227aded943e9fb08","tid":2319600,"uid":161726,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"84f1ec5920f042c1e4cb415102ebd9b7c5f386f4","tid":2319600,"uid":191926,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,